Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.52,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be back this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.48,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Don't drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.36,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I've played a fish before, \Nso I'll be totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:18.64,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what to make of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.81,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,So Sasuga-chan's into surfing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:25.62,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,That girl honestly does everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.28,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,She'll come back from a random walk saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:32.76,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,"A stranger taught me how\Nto do this thing." Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:36.88,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,The other day, it was pottery,\Nand before that, it was amateur radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.38,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\shad0\fs12\frz5.854\c&H77787A&\3c&HF0F3F2&\pos(164.001,232.667)}Sasuga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.38,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial\b1\fs12\frz2.168\3c&HF2F2F4&\c&H27252C&\pos(470.666,285.333)}Niizuma
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.25,0:02:42.00,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Currently, she's hooked on researching \Nmorning glories and surfing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:46.63,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I wonder if this is how she \Nprepares for her roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.17,Main - Top,Sasuga,0,0,0,,How'd ya like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:52.69,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You seem tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.21,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Did you stay up all night again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.30,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,It's summer vacay time for school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.92,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,and SIRIUS is on break until we \Nstart prepping for the fall show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:08.80,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,All righty! Another day of checking \Nout the chatter about us on the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:13.86,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Gotta make sure none\Nof those anti-fans get popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:20.96,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about this for a while,\N but Panda's kinda dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:29.13,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san? Good morn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.19,Main,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.68,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.27,Main,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.60,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I feel alive again. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.23,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.66,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It was the strangest thing.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.32,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Those bottles hold a clear liquid, like water,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:57.34,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(3000,1)\fnTimes New Roman\bord1\fs8\shad0\an7\c&H12111D&\3c&H7B8185&\b1\pos(451.999,124.666)}The Star of\NAsakusa
