Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.90,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,yet no matter how much I drink,\NI remain thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.23,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It just doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.20,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Ah, so you drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.77,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \Nshe does reek of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.67,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona, let's get some air in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:07.59,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:16.45,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I heard that you've been visiting \Nvarious troupes these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.73,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I have! I've been visiting an improv \Ntroupe with Kathrina-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.78,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,where we can participate on the fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:24.78,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,We're actually going again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.15,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,That sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.49,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:32.32,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Ever since {\i1}Arabian Knights{\i0},\NI've fallen even more in love with acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.21,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,It's just so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.84,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Must be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:42.88,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,If I didn't have summer vacation \Nhomework, I could've joined you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.05,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.89,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,What homework do you have today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.71,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It's calligraphy, so I came by \Nto have Shamo-san teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:54.46,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I have sewing for home ec. \NThe day after that, I have kanji drills...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.39,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I guess grade-schoolers\Nhave their own troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:07.19,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina-chan! We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.37,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.88,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What's up, Kathrina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.36,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:17.87,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,M-My mama just said... she's in Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.22,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.36,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Your mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.12,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.06,Main,Randos,0,0,0,,Theresa Griebel is seriously here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.38,Main,Randos,0,0,0,,What's a World Dai Star doing in Asakusa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.11,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.13,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Kathrina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.15,Subtitles,Sign,0,0,0,,It's been so long. I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.90,Subtitles,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(323,306)}Me too, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.86,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,S-So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.40,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That's a World Dai Star for you!\N Her aura's on another level!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.58,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,It's just backlighting, you dummies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.65,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:58.82,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you. \NI'm Theresa, Kathrina's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.12,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,You must be Kokona and Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.88,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Kathrina's told me all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.15,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Th-That's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.56,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.69,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.30,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:11.88,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,You can touch her and she can talk...\N Is she really a Sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.54,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.21,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Mama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.61,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Theresa-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:27.56,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. I was just so curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.65,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,What a curious Sense. \NWill wonders never cease?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.67,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Dugong-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.92,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Who's this little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:44.41,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... sort of a pet that belongs to SIRIUS.\NMaybe more like a mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.26,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Meet Dugong-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:51.92,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Dugong-chan tagged along when we \Nsaid we'd be meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:55.32,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Be careful. That rodent bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.51,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.66,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I guess the little critter likes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.33,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Totally wrapped around your finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.25,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You little rodent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:17.95,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,World class...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:24.39,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,So, why did you suddenly come to Japan?\N You're pretty busy, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:28.46,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Well, I got some free time\Nand wanted to see my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.71,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Is that the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:35.84,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Yes. Though sadly, I have\Nto leave tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:36.53,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.36,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.26,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Do you girls know a lot about Asakusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.49,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.09,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Then could you show me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:48.35,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste to come all the way to Japan \Nand not do anything touristy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.60,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:52.75,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,So with that settled, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.97,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I see you're as pushy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.88,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\shad0\c&H694A40&\3c&HEFF5F2&\pos(320,42.267)\b1}Kaminarimon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.89,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Okay, smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.75,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Why are we wearing yukatas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.88,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Because we look cute in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:18.26,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,People are {\i1}really{\i0} staring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:21.63,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Well, there's a World Dai Star here.\NWhat do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:25.71,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Come now! There's no time to waste relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.15,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Where are we going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.90,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Well, if you want the \Nreal Asakusa experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.37,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.66,Subtitles,Sign,0,0,0,,How traditional!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.15,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Goemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:45.03,Main,Fan,0,0,0,,Theresa-san! Can I get a picture, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.58,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.18,Main,SP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.89,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,As long as you don't mind these \Nfuture Dai Stars joining me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.44,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,There we go.
