Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.10,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,They're doing touristy things in Asakusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.25,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:53.87,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I imagine Theresa-san is dragging \NKokona and Shizuka around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.24,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Oh, it's for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:10:00.36,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,It's trending all over social media. \N"A World Dai Star appears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:08.54,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fs20\an8\c&H1C1A18&\3c&HE5E3E1&\shad0}World Dai Star\N{\fs14}-Yae Niizuma
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:04.06,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I wish I could've met Theresa-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:07.15,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,She contacted us saying that she \Nwanted a tour of SIRIUS,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.55,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,so you can meet her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:11.42,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Then let's head to SIRIUS immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.25,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,You need to do your homework first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.45,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:18.71,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I need to concentrate on my work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.51,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,"SIRIUS girls enjoying their day off!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.92,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Take that, antis! Behold my cuteness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.19,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,190)\an1\pos(118,112.667)\shad0\bord0\fnArial\c&H184041&\fs20\b1}Got us some dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.17,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,"Got us some dinner"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.97,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,The heck happened to surfing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,1)\fnArial\shad0\b1\frx-5\bord0\fs36\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(321.456,128.969)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.50,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:45.24,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kokona and Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.86,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,No problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:51.92,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Theresa-san, you didn't sweat at all... \Nin spite of the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:56.54,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,World Dai Stars don't sweat. \NThat's what my mama told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.25,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,She's {\i1}definitely{\i0} lying to you about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:03.01,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,But she's so beautiful that \NI'd actually believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.31,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:18.42,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I thought I'd be just like her immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.69,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.28,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.78,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you, Theresa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.55,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'm Noa Hiiragi. It's an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.15,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Thank you for looking after my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:43.74,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Our troupe extended an invitation to you,\N but I guess you turned us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.92,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I'm sad I can't perform with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:50.57,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I didn't think I was ready for it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.14,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.72,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Is Shamo here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:55.75,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,She's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.12,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Shamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.87,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Shamo! Shamo! Shamo! Shamo! Shamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:08.80,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,It's been ages, Theresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.36,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:13.94,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,I've missed you too. How long {\i1}has{\i0} it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:17.44,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Since before I married Tobias, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:20.50,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Since we costarred in {\i1}A Midsummer \NNight's Dream{\i0} in Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.76,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I played Puck and you played Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.05,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,What lovely memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:31.42,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,I clearly remember you throwing a fit \Nbecause {\i1}you{\i0} wanted to be Titania.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.99,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I could play the role beautifully now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.52,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,but I still can't live up to your Titania.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:41.50,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Yeesh, she's definitely a World Dai Star!\N Her aura's intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.41,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Super intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.04,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Is that what the kids say these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.19,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I came back in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:53.66,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Which do you think she'd like best as a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.65,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.91,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Maybe you should cook them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:07.06,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,This is a lovely stage\Nthat's hosted many actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.71,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I can feel its history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.43,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Your daughter's also working hard right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:13.72,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:17.46,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Thank you for letting her join your troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.35,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Kathrina's talent is what got her in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.44,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,though she seems to be having \Nsome growing pains now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.65,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:32.04,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you. \NMy name is Yae Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:35.42,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Yae! I saw your performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:36.15,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:39.05,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,As Princess Kaguya and the Genie of the Lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:43.56,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Your closing show for {\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0}\Nwas especially magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.79,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I-I'm honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:51.42,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,So, um... We have a favor \Nto ask you, Theresa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.82,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,What is it? An autograph? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:57.24,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'd love one! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:14:02.64,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Even just for a second... \Ncould we see you perform?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.52,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:09.59,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes! We wanted to see \Na World Dai Star's acting live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.78,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.31,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.27,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:28.01,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,If Noa will do it with me, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:28.94,Main,All,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.41,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,The boss and Theresa-san are \Ngoing to perform together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.94,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,That's too epic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.57,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.27,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Please, Hiiragi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.43,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,All right, just one scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.95,Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Yay! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.72,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're going to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:26.58,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,I'm the one who brought you here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:29.64,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,so that we could indulge \Nthis passion together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:34.75,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,Your heart is under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.03,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,You can never turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.31,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,You can never even glance back at the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.66,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,Give yourself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:53.31,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,What kind of desires will burn through us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:56.94,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,What kind of sweet temptations await us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:03.60,Main,Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,You were guiding me, \Nthough I understood nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.18,Main,Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,Yet now I am here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.92,Main,Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,I will never turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:13.69,Main,Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,It's finally begun... our passion play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.34,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom) and Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,It'll burn through us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.12,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,This is our final play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:34.98,Main,Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,The curtain rises!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:35.97,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,The final play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.21,Main,Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,The final performance draws near!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:42.55,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,We can no longer turn back, Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.14,Main,Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,Phantom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.18,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,What's your next line?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:51.37,Main,Theresa (Christine),0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:56.21,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,I should be the one to play Don Juan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.56,Main,Hiiragi (Phantom),0,0,0,,Come... Let us fall to hell together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.47,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I think that's about enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:16.83,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.59,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Oh, crap... I seriously thought I \Nwas at the opera house for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:33.45,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Me too, even without a set or costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:35.69,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,My heart is pounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.36,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,So that's how a World Dai Star performs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.02,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,She really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.45,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san was amazing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:47.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I think she was playing her part \Nso we'd all be looking at Theresa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.45,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,She was truly like a phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.96,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,But right there at the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.71,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,Come! Let us fall to hell together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.21,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:05.45,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,You sure got guts to imitate \Nthat right after seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.47,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Nerves of orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:07.93,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:11.30,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,U-U-Uh, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:17.77,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,It seems your Sense helps bring out \Nthe performance of your costars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.89,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I was able to give \Na show close to the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:22.50,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.80,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:28.50,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I got to experience what it's like to work\Nwith a World Dai Star's Sense again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:31.53,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It's so far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:35.49,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,The more you understand yourself, \Nthe more your Sense will evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.86,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:46.10,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,This was such a fun day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.78,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for spending \Nit with me, Kathrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.26,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You're not going to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:56.58,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I thought you came here to scold me for \Nwhat a disappointment I've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:19:00.14,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I've done nothing of note\N even after performing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:04.65,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,in {\i1}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i0},\N{\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0}, and {\i1}Romeo and Juliet{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:08.59,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'm only getting attention because I'm \Nthe daughter of a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:13.66,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I haven't left any deeper\N impression than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.10,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Even though Kokona has.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.58,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,But you haven't been\Ncutting corners, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:23.65,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.50,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Then I don't see a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.19,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,You're doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.53,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:38.25,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,The reason I came to SIRIUS is to discuss \Nthe future of Kathrina Griebel's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:39.96,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,My work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.69,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,You've received a number \Nof offers from various troupes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:44.68,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.55,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,They've seen your SIRIUS performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:52.82,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,They know about your mishap in \NGermany, but they still want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.96,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,B-But that's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:02.37,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Opportunities appear all the time \Nbefore you're actually ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:06.00,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Is there a reason you have to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:09.24,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I'll get you the papers \Nfrom the troupes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:12.48,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,Give me your answer by the \Ntime I leave Japan tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.72,Main,Theresa,0,0,0,,I'll honor your wishes, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.12,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:59.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\shad0\bord0\fnArial\c&H184041&\fs20\b1\pos(140.667,106)}I'll become a Dai Star at SIRIUS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:44.26,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,Our next performance will be \Nour last chance this year
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:47.70,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,to get the World Theatre League\N to recognize a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:52.56,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,Still, we've never had so much trouble \Ndeciding on our fall show before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:55.57,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,The reasonable decision is to go with Yae.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.54,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,Her acting skills are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:00.31,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,But Panda's not too shabby either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:04.54,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I mean, she's so adorable, her Sense is \Nsuper awesome, and she's got plenty of fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.00,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,We'll just have to go with Panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:09.41,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I'd really like that, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:11.82,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Don't take me seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:13.45,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:20.45,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Our upcoming fall production will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:23.72,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Phantom of the Opera{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:31.24,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,And we'll be holding auditions\Nfor the role of the Phantom.
